name: Aegean
description: Native to the Greek islands known as the Cyclades in the Aegean Sea, these are natural cats, meaning they developed without humans getting involved in their breeding.

name: Bengal
description: The Bengal cat is highly active and intelligent. They are constantly moving, playing, and seeking interaction with their owners.

name: Siamese
description: Siamese cats are well known for their striking blue almond-shaped eyes, short coat, and large ears.

name: Abyssinian
description: Abyssinians are one of the oldest known cat breeds. They are curious, energetic, and love to explore their surroundings.

name: Persian
description: Persians are known for their calm and affectionate personality, as well as their long, luxurious coat.

name: Maine Coon
description: The Maine Coon is one of the largest domesticated cat breeds. They are known for their friendly and intelligent nature.
